  <brief_title>Interactions Between Intravenous (IV) Cocaine and Lofexidine</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase 1, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled Assessment of Potential Interactions Between Intravenous Cocaine and Lofexidine</official_title>
  <sponsors>
