  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to assess potential interactions between intravenous (IV)
      cocaine and treatment with lofexidine.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      To determine the safety of daily oral lofexidine alone and concurrent with IV cocaine
      infusions of 20 mg and 40 mg in cocaine-experienced, non-opiate-addicted volunteers.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
